description: The Share Class is a share class of a Fund which aims to achieve a return on your investment, through a combination of capital growth and income on the Fund’s assets, which reflects the return of the MSCI World Minimum Volatility Advanced Select Index, the Fund’s benchmark index (Index). The Share Class, via the Fund, is passively managed and invests in equity securities (e.g. shares) that, so far as possible and practicable, make up the Index.
name: iShares Edge MSCI World Minimum Volatility Advanced UCITS ETF
